page.title: 06SATURDAY TELEVISION 1985.
page.content: Some of the programmes broadcast by the B.B.C. and recieved in Keighley on Saturday{June 15th 1985. { }BBC1 8.30am{Saturday Picture Show.}Music and cartoons for children. 12.15pm{Grandstand.}News of the days sport. 5.25pm {Wonder Woman.}A fantasy series from the U.S.A. 8.10pm {Dynasty.}A popular soap opera from the U.S.A. 10.00pm{The Royal International Horse { Show.}Major showjumping event. BBC2 4.30pm {Cricket.}The day's cricket. 7.30pm {Trooping the Colour.}The Queen's birthday. 9.00pm {The Godfather II.}A film about the Mafia. 12.45am{International Tennis.}A look at the days tennis.
